OptionDescription
ACROSShoot in Black and White In rich details with sharpness. Available with yellow (Ye), red (R), and green (G) filters, which deepen shades of gray corresponding to hues complementary to the selected color. ● AY ACROS+Ye FILTER: Slightly enhances contrast and darkens skies. ● AR ACROS+R FILTER: Enhances contrast and darkens skies considerably.
